import { Button } from '@mui/material'
import React, { Fragment } from 'react'


function MenusCointeiner() {
    return (
        <Fragment className='container'>
           <section> <Button
               color='secondary'
               id="Desayuno"
               variant="contained"
               margin="large"
               type="submit"
               data-testid='Desayuno'
               onClick={window.location.href='/desayuno'}>Desayuno
               

                
            </Button>
            <Button
               color='secondary'
               id="AlmuerzoCena"
               variant="contained"
               margin="large"
               type="submit"
               data-testid='Desayuno'>Almuerzo y Cena

                
            </Button>
            </section>
           
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default MenusCointeiner
